try {
    await page.goto(`${address}/task-web/#/task/cinema`, {
        timeout: 0
    })

    await page.setViewport({
        width: 1920,
        height: 722
    })
    //新增任务
    await page.waitForSelector('.el-form-item > .el-form-item__content > .el-dropdown > .el-button > span')

    await page.waitFor(2000)
    //咪咕影院购票任务
    await page.waitForSelector('body > .el-dropdown-menu > .el-dropdown-menu__item:nth-child(1)')
    await page.click('body > .el-dropdown-menu > .el-dropdown-menu__item:nth-child(1)')
    takescreenshot('影院任务列表-点击新增任务按钮')
    await page.waitFor(2000)
    //任务名称
    await page.waitForSelector('.el-row:nth-child(2) > .fields > .el-form-item > .el-form-item__content > .el-input > .el-input__inner')
    await page.type('.el-row:nth-child(2) > .fields > .el-form-item > .el-form-item__content > .el-input > .el-input__inner','test')

    await page.waitFor(2000)
   
     //任务结束时间
     await page.waitForSelector('.fields:nth-child(4) > .el-form-item > .el-form-item__content > .el-date-editor > .el-input__inner')
